Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Italian elections
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03zjkqg
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 27 Jun 1976
Relief in the West as Italy's Communist Party fails to make the electoral gains it had hoped for. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less